        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks for new [6th] edition of <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi>.</p> 
            <p>Is working on Echini.</p>
            <p>The more material he gets the less easy it is to diagnose a genus or species. Has little doubt that "classification is nothing but the most arbitrary convenient tool, depending upon the material at our command at a special time".</p>
        </abstract>
